content:
@{ 
    string culture = ViewBag.culture;
    string assetFolder = "/mix-content/assets/aaa";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="@ViewBag.culture">

<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no' name='viewport' />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
    <title>
        @ViewBag.Title
    </title>
<!-- 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/assets/css/shared.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/assets/css/app-vendor.min.css" /> -->
    <base href="/@ViewBag.culture">

    <!-- CSS Files -->
    <link href="@assetFolder/css/material-kit.css?v=2.0.4" rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Fonts and icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500,700|Roboto+Slab:400,700|Material+Icons" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/latest/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.quilljs.com/1.3.6/quill.snow.css">
    
    @RenderSection("Schema", false)     
    
    @RenderSection("Seo", false)     
    <!--[STYLES]-->
    @RenderSection("Styles", false)    
    
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/core/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>

<body class="@ViewData["PageClass"] sidebar-collapse" ng-app="MixClient" ng-controller="AppClientController" ng-init="init('@ViewBag.culture')">    
    
    @RenderBody()   

    <partial name="../Widgets/SubscribeModal.cshtml"/>
    <partial name="../Widgets/ContactUsModal.cshtml"/>


    <!--   Core JS Files   -->
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/core/popper.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/core/bootstrap-material-design.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/plugins/moment.min.js"></script>
    <!--	Plugin for the Datepicker, full documentation here: https://github.com/Eonasdan/bootstrap-datetimepicker -->
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/plugins/bootstrap-datetimepicker.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <!--  Plugin for the Sliders, full documentation here: http://refreshless.com/nouislider/ -->
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/plugins/nouislider.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <!--  Google Maps Plugin  -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=YOUR_KEY_HERE"></script>
    <!-- Place this tag in your head or just before your close body tag. -->
    <script async defer src="https://buttons.github.io/buttons.js"></script>
    <!-- Control Center for Material Kit: parallax effects, scripts for the example pages etc -->
    <script src="@assetFolder/js/material-kit.js?v=2.0.4" type="text/javascript"></script>

    @RenderSection("Scripts", false)

</body>
</html>
